						</additions>
						<bindingDesc>
							<binding>
								<p>Post-1600, brown leather, blind-tooled, with remains of clasps.</p>
								<p>Spine title: 'I. Bereshith Rabbah. II. Siphra. III. Siphre. IV. Petirath Aharon u-Mosheh. Hebrew &amp; Aramaic. Brit. Mus. Additional 16.406.'</p>
